    "intro": "Interpretation moves from what Song of Solomon 4 says to what it means — situating the chapter within the canonical debate about its genre, tracking the author's argument through the three literary movements, and surfacing the theological claims that bind this chapter to the rest of Scripture. The most contested question in the study of Song of Solomon is the relationship between its literal and its allegorical registers, and that question must be addressed honestly before the movements below can be read rightly.",
